                       Finder - By Stefan Lindström

        A small tool for finding out whether a device/volume/assign
          exists or not. Prolly most useful for autoamted scripts
     when you don't watch the machine and don't want it to hang around
          waiting for you to remove the requester for VOLUME xxx:




